=== Whiteout ===
* 1. Choice, ''''Maximize propulsion.'''', {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2 or ''''Release a drone.'''', {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 4. Gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}.
* 2a. Maximise propulsion, narrative, gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}.
* 2b. Release a drone, narrative, gives {{iconify|Physics}} Research.
* 3. Choice, ''''Take a sample'''', {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6, or ''''Trace a map'''', {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 3. Gives {{reward|ast|ast2|empty|empty}}.
* 4a. Take a sample, narrative, gives {{iconify|Rare crystals}}.
* 4b. Trace a map, narrative, gives {{iconify|Society}} Research.
* 5. Narrative, gives {{reward|ast|ast3|empty|empty}} and a modifier granting +10% {{iconify|Physics}} Research for ten years.
